high_descs: Take a step to your right then walk to the counter in front of you then turn right and walk to the fridge.
Open the freezer and grab the glass from behind the egg then close the door.
Turn around and walk to the counter then turn right.
Put the cup in the sink then full it with water and pick it back up remembering to shut off the tap.
Turn left and take a step to your left then look up.
Open the cupboard in front of you and put the cup full of water up there then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled cup of water in the cupboard.

high_descs: Walk forward, then hang a right around the kitchen island, stopping at the fridge.
Remove the cup on the lowest shelf in the freezer.
Turn around and walk forwards to the sink.
Put the cup in the sink and fill it with water, picking it back up.
Turn around and walk towards the stove, facing the right cabinet above the stove.
Set the cup of water on the lower shelf of the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Fill a cup from the freezer with water, put it in the cabinet over the stove.

high_descs: take the black cup out of the fridge
take the cup to the sink
take the cup of water to the stove and dump it in the pot
put the cup in the cabinet above the stove
anns.task_desc: get a glass from the fridge, fill it with water for a pot, then put it away.
